run(sql="
with b as (
  select
    distinct pogPlSupcMaster as pogId
  from
    plSupcMaster
),

  select distinct pogId
from `all(dProduct)`
where lower(brandName) in ('nbox',
'hometales',
'fitmonkey',
'rangita',
'style smith',
'miyuki',
'9lives',
'tenderbeans',
'urbanmark',
'aragma',
'nord')
)

select To_date(From_unixtime((orderDate) / 1000)) as orderDate,
count(distinct subOrderId) as suborders,
count(distinct case when b_pogId is not null  then subOrderId else null end) as pl_suborders,
count(distinct case when c_pogId is not null  then subOrderId else null end) as true_pl_suborders,
count(distinct case when Ftu_orderId is not null then subOrderId else null end) as ftu_suborders,
count(distinct case when b_pogId is not null and Ftu_orderId is not null then subOrderId else null end) as pl_ftu_suborders,
sum(NM) as FB_NM,
sum(NM)/count(distinct subOrderId) as PL_NMBO
from
(
select a.subOrderId,max(a.orderDate) as orderDate,max(b.pogId) as b_pogId,max(c.pogId) as c_pogId,max(ft.orderId) as Ftu_orderId,
max(econ1.NMIncAd) as NM

from `all(agCmDump)` a

join `temp.final_attri2` at
on at.subOrderId=a.subOrderId
and lower(at.Channel) LIKE '%fb%'
and 
    (lower(at.utmContent) like '%plfeed%'
    or lower(at.utmCampaign) like '%plfeed%'
    )
and To_date(From_unixtime((a.orderDate) / 1000)) >= '2022-05-01'
left join `temp.FTUs`ft
on at.orderId=ft.orderId

left join b
on a.pogId=b.pogId
and To_date(From_unixtime((a.orderDate) / 1000)) >= '2022-05-01'

left join c
on a.pogId=c.pogId
and To_date(From_unixtime((a.orderDate) / 1000)) >= '2022-05-01'

and To_date(From_unixtime((a.orderDate) / 1000)) >= '2022-05-01'
where To_date(From_unixtime((a.orderDate) / 1000)) >= '2022-05-01'
group by a.subOrderId
) a
group by orderDate
having sum(NM) is not null
order by orderDate desc
